reviewText: I was happy I found the movie for my daughter. But very disappointed when we went to watch it, it was scratched and would skip and freeze so we were unable to watch it.
Too corny; didn't let it finish.
really enjoyed this movie with grandaughter.
Rough, even for a kids show.  Even my kid who loves everything just thought it was ok...
Kids really enjoyed it. Arrived in good shape
Very entertaining to 7 and 8 year olds

last night we had 4 kids 8 & 9 years old watch this movie and they all enjoyed it, and watched it again in the morning. it's nice to watch a movie without sass talk and the usual bathroom humor (which I do enjoy from time-to-time but it does get old).
